**Synopsis:**

Generate the answer `ans` one step at a time by accumulating the total sum of the `K` values adjacent to-the-right of each `i`<sup>th</sup> element of the input array `A`.  To simplify the code when `K` is negative, simply reverse `A` and return the reversed answer using positive `K`.

